metadata.name: ElevenFold - VV
metadata.description:
Most of us don't have 2.25BTC to hand over to YugaVault.  
ElevenFold - VV is an alternative for everyone that believed they had a chance.  
On Yuga's reveal day, burn your ElevenFold - VV and receive your unique ElevenFold art piece, inspired by the designs provided by Yuga. 
Everybody should be able to participate in drops, not just the 300 biggest whales.
